<item>
            <title>[THRIFT-3020] Cannot compile thrift as C++03</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/THRIFT-3020</link>
                <project id="12310800" key="THRIFT">Thrift</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Thrift no longer compiles under C++03, given the recent fix for &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/THRIFT-2937&quot; title=&quot;Allow setting a maximum frame size in TFramedTransport&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;THRIFT-2937&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;THRIFT-2937&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;. This is due to the way a field is initialized with a default value.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The compilation error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;Error 1 error C2864: &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;apache::thrift::transport::TFramedTransport::maxFrameSize_&apos;&lt;/span&gt; : only &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;static&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; integral data members can be initialized within a &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;class &lt;/span&gt;D:\dev\thrift\lib\cpp\src\thrift\transport\TBufferTransports.h 404 1 thrift_static
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
                <environment>&lt;p&gt;Visual Studio 2010&lt;/p&gt;</environment>
